”号、“托莱多”号和英国海军“辉煌”号核潜艇曾出现在该海域。俄罗斯“News24”新闻网曾报道，俄罗斯国防部曾向美国五角大楼申请调查“孟菲斯”号和“托莱多”号核潜艇，但是被拒绝，英国方面的回复也如此。俄北方舰队前司令：“库尔斯克”号核潜艇沉没原因为与北约潜艇相撞"},"attached_info":"Cj8I2c3H0L3mhowMEAMaCDczNTc0NTU4IIPU7YwGMAk4yQJAMHIJNTAwODE4NzEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"35 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-33fe28718c6d2885ae2d0abc3a06aaa4_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1637737749.256007","card_id":"Q_266462404","target":{"id":266462404,"title":"下雪天为什么这么浪漫？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/266462404","type":"question","created":1517388547,"answer_count":236,"follower_count":309,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[22959],"comment_count":6,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I2c3H0L3mhowMEAMaCDIxMDE3MTU5IIOGxtMFMAY4tQJAMXIJMjY2NDYyNDA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"33 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-331fb4fa29ab4430954bf91e369d57eb_720w.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2021-11-24 15:09:09"}}